  <brief_title>Increasing Folate Status of a General Population(FOLSUPP STUDY)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects Of A Mixed Diet Intervention Versus Folic Acid Supplementation And Metafolin® Supplementation On Folate Status And Cardiovascular Disease Risk Factors In Healthy Adults</official_title>
